<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #059669; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
      .footer { padding: 15px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
      .achievement-box { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #059669; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
      .button { background: #059669; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 5px; }
      .info-row { margin: 8px 0; }
      .label { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
      .approval-info { background: #e6fffa; border: 1px solid #059669; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>🎯 L2 Achievement Approval Required</h2>
        <p>Already Approved by L1</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear L2 Manager,</p>
        
        <p>An achievement has been approved by L1 and now requires your L2 approval. Please review and approve/return the submission.</p>
        
        <div class="achievement-box">
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Employee:</span> <%= @employee.employee_name %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Employee Code:</span> <%= @employee.employee_code %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Email:</span> <%= @employee.employee_email %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Department:</span> <%= @department.department_name %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Activity:</span> <%= @user_detail.activity.activity_name %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Month:</span> <%= @achievement.month.capitalize %>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">Status:</span> Achievement approved by L1, ready for L2 approval
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="approval-info">
          <h4>L1 Approval Details:</h4>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="label">L1 Status:</span> Approved - Please log in to view L1 remarks and percentage
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please log in to the system to review and approve this achievement.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Review the employee's achievement submission and L1 feedback</li>
          <li>Add your L2 remarks and percentage if needed</li>
          <li>Approve to send to L3, or Return with feedback</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated notification from KRA App</p>
        <p>Please do not reply to this email</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
